        "product_description": {
            "value": "GEAR AID Tenacious Tape Flex Patches deliver ultra-strong, flexible repairs for vinyl and synthetic fabric gear. Repair a tear in a PVC inflatable, vinyl furniture seat, air mattress, awning, tent, sail, canopy, or other outdoor gear with a durable, weatherproof patch. These peel-and-stick patches make nearly invisible repairs to all types of vinyl and synthetic fabric materials — no sewing or iron-on application required. The heavy-duty patch stretches and flexes with fabric and is resistant to punctures for a permanent repair you can count on. Backed by a strong adhesive, this repair kit is easy to bring along in your pack. Each pack includes two 3\" x 5\" clear, pre-cut patches for quick, waterproof fixes at home or on the trail. Packaging may vary.",
